-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸªœ Steps to Create First Web Page

Step 1: Create a File

* File name: `index.html`
* Extension must be `.html`

---

Step 2: Write HTML Code

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>My First Web Page</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Hello World</h1>
</body>
</html>
```

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ” Code Explanation

* `<!DOCTYPE html>` â†’ Declares HTML5
* `<html>` â†’ Root element
* `<head>` â†’ Page information (title)
* `<title>` â†’ Browser tab name
* `<body>` â†’ Visible content
* `<h1>` â†’ Heading (Hello World)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

â–¶ï¸ How to Run the Web Page

1. Save the file
2. Right-click â†’ **Open with Browser**
3. Browser displays **Hello World**

âœ” Congratulations! Your first web page is live ğŸ‰

