```

ğŸ“Œ `<h1>` â†’ Bigger text
ğŸ“Œ `<p>` â†’ Normal paragraph

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âŒ Common Beginner Mistakes

* Forgetting `.html` extension
* Missing opening or closing tags
* Writing code outside `<body>`
* Saving file incorrectly

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

* Always use `<!DOCTYPE html>`
* Use proper indentation
* Save file before refreshing browser
* Use meaningful titles

